      • voidTransactionStatus

        public java.lang.String voidTransactionStatus
        Indicates the Void status of a Charge Transaction. Valid values are V (is a void request), S (void submitted for this transaction), R (is a forced refund request), C (closed error record, already recreated) and null.

      • callForAuthorizationStatus

        public java.lang.String callForAuthorizationStatus
        Indicates the Call for Authorization status for the Charge Transaction. Valid Values: REQUIRES_CALL - If a call for Authorization is required. AUTH_CODE_ACQUIRED - Authorization Code has been acquired. CLOSED - Once the gateway has been communicated with and the funds have been transferred via the normal means.
